  <para>
    &productname; comes with several sources of information and documentation,
    many of which are already integrated into your installed system.
  </para>
  <para>
    To enter the Help of &gnome; or &libo; directly from an application,
    click the <guilabel>Help</guilabel> button or press <keycap>F1</keycap> key.
    Both options take you directly to the application's documentation in the
    help center.
  </para>
  <para>
    You can also start the Help of &gnome; by opening a terminal end entering
    <command>yelp</command> or from the main menu by clicking <menuchoice>
    <guimenu>Applications</guimenu><guimenu>Favorites</guimenu>
    <guimenu>Help</guimenu></menuchoice>.
  </para>
