      <para>
        For more information on how to work with
        <productname>&gnome; Desktop</productname>, see
        <link xlink:href="https://help.gnome.org"></link>.
      </para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        For more information on how to work with &libo;, see
